Source-derived reference material
---------------------------------

This repository contains original skill/playbook text plus reference notes and
source extracts derived from third-party vendor documentation, community posts,
blogs, and support articles. The MIT license above applies to original repository
contributions only. Third-party source excerpts, URLs, product names, command
syntax, and vendor documentation remain subject to their original owners' terms.

The source-derived reference files are included for local operational context,
attribution, and verification. Before redistributing, bundling commercially, or
publishing a derivative catalog, review the upstream licenses/terms for any
included reference extract and replace long excerpts with citations or concise
notes where required.
